posts.title: Send Me Some Prayers Pedes
posts.content:
Went to the doctor this morning for a full physical. My BP is 211 over 136. Then they got the EKG results and it turns out I had a minor/silent heart attack recently. My doctor was shocked. “How are you walking around? You need to be in a hospital!” I hate going to the doctor. So now I have to check myself into to the hospital for 3-4 days so they can run all the tests on me and try and bring my BP down. Hopefully it’s nothing serious. I’m a pure blood so it’s not the clot shot.

Pray it’s nothing serious because I don’t want to miss the next 4 years.

Thanks everyone who reads this.

posts.title: Send Me Some Prayers Pedes
posts.content:
Went to the doctor this morning for a full physical. My BP is 211 over 136. Then they got the EKG results and it turns out I had a minor/silent heart attack recently. My doctor was shocked. “How are you walking around? You need to be in a hospital!” I hate going to the doctor. So now I have to check myself into to the hospital for 3-4 days so they can run all the tests on me and try and bring my BP down. Hopefully it’s nothing serious. I’m a pure blood so it’s not the clot shot.

Pray it’s nothing serious because I don’t want to miss the next 4 years.

Thanks everyone who reads this.
